item.title: Teleport help
item.dc:creator: @NewbieNewty Newty
item.description:
@NewbieNewty wrote:

[quote=“Elven Dremor, post:7, topic:283297”]In clickingmost.java

Add:

case 50245: c.teleEffect = 1; c.sendQuest("TITLE HERE", 2470); c.sendQuest("Dagg Lair", 2471); c.sendQuest("LOW LVL TRAINING", 2472); c.sendQuest("Slayer Tower", 2473); c.sendFrame164(2469); break;

Then:

Dagg Lair Cords:

case 9167: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(XXXX+misc.random(2), YYYY+misc.random(2), 0); c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); c.frame61(0); if(c.teleEffect == 2) c.triggerTele(XXXX+misc.random(2), YYYY+misc.random(2), 0); c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); c.frame61(0); break;

LOW LVL TRAINING Cords:

case 9168: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(XXXX, YYYY, 0); c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); if(c.teleEffect == 2) c.closeInterface(); break;

Slayer Tower Cords:

case 9169: if(c.teleEffect == 1) c.triggerTele(XXXX+misc.random(2), YYYY+misc.random(2), 0); c.killMyNPCs(); c.resetfollowers(); c.frame61(0); break;

Rep Plawkz.[/quote]

Don’t ask for rep, it is against the forum rules.
